---
// Componente Astro: LaMatriz
// No recibe props por ahora, es una sección estática de la landing
---

<section id="servicios" class="px-4 lg:px-40 flex justify-center py-10">
  <div class="layout-content-container flex flex-col max-w-[1200px] flex-1">

    <!-- Header de sección -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-end gap-6 p-4 mb-8">
      <div class="flex min-w-72 flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
          <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
          Red Neuronal Activa
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-white text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.04em] font-display uppercase">
          LA MATRIZ:<br />SERVICIOS
        </h1>
        <p class="text-primary/70 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Ingeniería del futuro de la interacción digital a través de computación espacial de alta fidelidad y arquitecturas de software a escala galáctica.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-4">
        <div class="text-right hidden sm:block">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Carga del Sistema</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-mono text-primary">0.00042ms</p>
        </div>
        <button class="flex min-w-[160px] items-center justify-center rounded-xl h-12 px-6 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white text-sm font-bold hover:bg-white/10 transition-all uppercase tracking-wider">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined mr-2 text-primary">sensors</span>
          Sistema en Línea
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid principal de servicios -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-4 p-4">

      <div class="md:col-span-8 group relative overflow-hidden glass-card rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[120px]">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-primary/30">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">code</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Web</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg max-w-md leading-relaxed">
            Motores personalizados de alto rendimiento construidos con Next.js y computación perimetral distribuida. Diseñamos para velocidad, escala y seguridad absoluta.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-bold">Activo</span>
          <span class="text-white/40 text-xs font-mono">TIPO_NODO: CORE_WEB</span>
          <button class="ml-auto text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline flex items-center gap-2">
            Ver Detalles <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4 glass-card rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]">
        <div>
          <div class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-primary/30 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">phone_iphone</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Aplicaciones</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            Conectividad a escala galáctica para iOS y Android utilizando cimientos nativos y arquitecturas multiplataforma de alta eficiencia.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Activo</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer hover:text-primary transition-colors">Explorar Tecnología</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Cards secundarias -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 glass-card rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
        <div>
          <div class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-primary/30 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">view_in_ar</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">AR/VR</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Experiencias espaciales inmersivas que redefinen las fronteras físicas y digitales.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
          <div class="text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">Módulo_Estereoscópico</div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40 text-sm">open_in_new</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4 glass-card rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
        <div>
          <div class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-primary/30 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">sports_esports</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Videojuegos</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Mecánicas interactivas de grado AAA y motores de física avanzada para gaming de próxima generación.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
          <div class="text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">Física_En_Línea</div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40 text-sm">rocket_launch</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4 glass-card rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
        <div>
          <div class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-primary/30 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">layers</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">XR</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Fusión fluida de realidades físicas y digitales en un flujo operativo único y coherente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
          <div class="text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">Sinc_Realidad_01</div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40 text-sm">hub</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
